about.summary: Building applications with LLMs through composability

name: langchain
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "langchain" %}
{% set version = "0.0.334" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  - url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/langchain-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: 76fff43602fd284e86dd38c8fcdcbc036d3d26178d1335148bcc22964a6879b4
  - url: https://github.com/langchain-ai/{{ name }}/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: 79a68c33bde30c7a90eba698938c082ee83f8ee04cbb686eeb1f26ae0ce9870f
    folder: github-source

build:
  entry_points:
    - langchain-server = langchain.server:main
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.8,<4.0
    - poetry-core >=1.0.0
    - pip
  run:
    - anyio <4.0
    - jsonpatch >=1.33.0,<2.0.0
    - google-api-core >=2.11.1,<3.0.0
    - python >=3.8.1,<4.0
    - pydantic >=1,<3
